<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ shì huǒ, diǎn rán zhǎn zhǎn xī miè de dēng.
 zhǔ a nǐ shì dēng, zhào liàng hēi yè nán xíng de lù.
 zhǔ a nǐ shì lù, yǐn dǎo wǒ men zǒu xiàng guāng míng.
 zhǔ nǐ shì shì shàng de guāng, zhào liàng quán shì jiè.
 cóng cǐ yǒu le zhēn ài, cóng cǐ yǒu le gē shēng.
 cóng cǐ yǒu le zhēn lǐ, cóng cǐ yǒu le shēng mìng.
 cóng cǐ yǒu le kuān róng, cóng cǐ yǒu le dì xiōng.
 cóng cǐ yǒu le gǎn dòng, cóng cǐ yǒu le gòng míng.
 zhǔ a wǒ men zàn měi nǐ bǎo guì de shèng míng.
 jiàn zhèng rén rú yún fèn yǒng qián xíng, dōu shì nǐ qīn shǒu zuò chéng.
 dào tiān yá hǎi yú, chuán yáng nǐ qí miào de míng.
 zhè shì wǒ men yī shēng de shǐ mìng, yī shēng de shǐ mìng. a a.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ men yào chuán yáng nǐ qí miào de míng 迦南1002</title>
<hymn_number>1002</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>